headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid DOV and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Dover has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 22.8%. The stock now trades at $233.50, marking a 29.4% gain. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
